        "source_line_end": 153,
        "raw_title": "Multi-domain two-skill section composer",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Test posts a query that classifies into two skills and expects the SSE done event within 30 s with a body containing exactly two `## ` headings in classifier order. The test times out before any event arrives.\n- **Hypothesis:** Wave-D fix C-1 wired the per-skill composer; the same test passed at FINAL. Stack likely stale; bounce and re-test before opening a code bug.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py` (`run_orchestrator_streaming`, `_wrap_with_skill_sections`), `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/chat_router.py`",
        "hinted_priority": "P0",
        "hinted_assignee": null,
