        "raw_title": "Three-skill multi-domain",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Three classified skills should each render their own `## ` heading. Times out.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stale stack.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py`",
