      "enriched": {
        "bug_id": "2f9524f12b2ed261",
        "summary": "Typo-tolerant CoreWeave queries are not routed through project_status and time out without tool errors",
        "description_md": "### Symptom\nA query like `what's going on with corweave` does not resolve to CoreWeave through the `project_status` skill. The reported outcome is a timeout, with zero `tool_traces` rows at `status=error`.\n\n### Where\n- `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py:369-373` — skill section title mapping includes `project_status` and `project_status_summary`.\n- Nearby routing/classification logic in `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py` determines which app/skill path is taken before any tool execution.\n\n### Code snippet\n```python\n_SKILL_SECTION_TITLES = {\n    \"project_status\": \"Project Status\",\n    \"project_status_summary\": \"Project Status\",\n    \"email_triage\": \"Email Triage\",\n    \"email_summary\": \"Email Triage\",\n    \"deviation_analysis\": \"Deviation Analysis\",\n    \"deviation_summary\": \"Deviation Analysis\",\n    \"risk_analysis\": \"Risk Analysis\",\n    \"risk_summary\": \"Risk Analysis\",\n    \"meeting_summary\": \"Meeting Summary\",\n    \"meeting_notes\": \"Meeting Summary\",\n}\n```\n\n### Reproduction steps\n1. Send the chat query `what's going on with corweave`.\n2. Observe that the request does not resolve to CoreWeave via the `project_status` skill.\n3. Check observability data for the run.\n4. Observe that the run times out and no `tool_traces` rows are recorded with `status=error`.\n\n### Expected behavior\nThe typo-tolerant entity match resolves `corweave` to CoreWeave, and the request is handled through the `project_status` skill without timing out.\n\n### Actual behavior\nThe query does not complete successfully; it times out instead of producing a CoreWeave `project_status` result.\n\n### Last toucher\navivriftin5 on 2026-05-03\n\n### Related\n- `tests/centprojects-tool-trace-failing.md` contains a nearby failing trace for a typo query involving `corweave`.\n- `apps/centralbackend/app/admin/llm_usage.py` reads `tool_traces` for run inspection.\n- `_core` commit `b7801f5e483b3156475d1279ac10d8fe3159095a` is the last toucher for the suspicious lines.",
        "reproduction_steps": [
          {
            "order": 1,
            "text": "Send the chat query `what's going on with corweave`."
          },
          {
            "order": 2,
            "text": "Observe that the request does not resolve to CoreWeave via the `project_status` skill."
          },
          {
            "order": 3,
            "text": "Check observability data for the run."
          },
          {
            "order": 4,
            "text": "Observe that the run times out and no `tool_traces` rows are recorded with `status=error`."
          }
        ],
        "expected_behavior": "The typo-tolerant query resolves to CoreWeave through the project_status skill and completes without timing out.",
        "actual_behavior": "The query times out instead of resolving to CoreWeave, and no successful project_status handling is observed.",
