        "raw_title": "15-second heartbeat keepalive",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** When a graph node is silent > 15 s, the orchestrator should emit a `heartbeat` event every 10 s ±1 s. Times out at 30 s.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stale stack — heartbeat code shipped in a prior wave.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py`",
