        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Across the suite, every event type in the documented vocabulary (`search_start`, `tool_call`, `tool_result`, `token`, `personal_context`, `personal_context_applied`, `enrichment_complete`, `skills_loaded`, `flow_suggestion`, `skill_start`, `skill_end`, `skill_error`, `compose_start`, `done`, `error`) should have been observed at least once. Test sets up the full coverage probe and times out.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stale stack.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py`",
