        "source_line_end": 204,
        "raw_title": "Swipe-right pin gesture",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Test asserts the UI fires a `POST /api/sessions/{id}/pin` from a swipe-right touch handler. Pin endpoint exists in the backend; the frontend touch-event handler is unimplemented.\n- **Affected files (likely):** centralfrontend's session-list component and a touch-gesture utility module.",
        "hinted_priority": "P3",
        "hinted_assignee": null,
        "hinted_repos": [
          "_core"
        ],
