        "raw_title": "Full dispatch fires all six SMEs",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Test posts a request that touches every pillar (Network/Storage/Power/Physical/Security/Operations) and expects one `orchestrator_start` + six `agent_start` + six `agent_end` events within 30 s. Times out at 30 s.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stack staleness (was passing at FINAL); also possible the LLM cassette for the 6-SME parallel run is missing or stale. Bounce and re-record.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centarb_backend/app/agent/orchestrator.py` (or equivalent — check `apps/centarb_backend/app/agent.py` for the multi-SME dispatch)",
        "hinted_priority": "P0",
        "hinted_assignee": null,
        "hinted_repos": [
          "vibe_coding/centarb"
        ],
        "hinted_components": [],
        "hinted_files": [
          "apps/centarb_backend/app/agent/orchestrator.py",
          "apps/centarb_backend/app/agent.py"
        ],
        "labels": [
          "timeout-suspected-stale"
        ],
        "inherited_module": {
          "repo_alias": "vibe_coding/centarb",
          "branch": "2026-05-03_Auto_Fixes",
          "commit_sha": "7cfb1e0",
          "repo_url": null
        },
        "closed_section": false,
