        "raw_title": "Single chat populates 8 trace tables joinable by `trace_id`",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Test posts a single chat and expects ≥ 1 row in each of the 8 documented trace tables (`orchestrator_runs`, `llm_runs`, `tool_traces`, `a2a_traces`, `audit_logs`, `classification_traces`, plus two Cent-App-side trace tables) all joinable by `trace_id`. Times out at 30 s.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stale stack. Fix C-17 (trace_id propagation migration) shipped — table schema is correct on FINAL.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py` (trace_id seeding) plus the 5 trace-models touched in fix C-17",
        "hinted_priority": "P1",
        "hinted_assignee": null,
        "hinted_repos": [],
