        "raw_title": "First chat response token p95 ≤ 5 s",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Performance probe — first content token must arrive within 5 s p95. Times out at 30 s, so first token never arrives.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stale stack or LLM provider latency. Bounce + re-run.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/graph.py`, `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/agent.py`",
        "hinted_priority": "P2",
