        "raw_title": "Rate limit boundary 30 chat / 60 s",
        "raw_body": "- **What's broken:** Test posts exactly 30 chat messages in 60 s (all should 200), then a 31st (should 429 with `Retry-After`), then waits past the window and posts a 32nd (should 200). Times out at 30 s — likely the very first chat in the burst is hanging.\n- **Hypothesis:** Stale stack; closely related to X-PERF-002.\n- **Affected files (likely):** `apps/centralbackend/app/orchestrator/chat_router.py` (`check_chat_rate_limit`)",
